<doc id="449419" wikidata="Q57368" url="?curid=449419" title="Districts of Botswana">
<text>Botswana is divided into ten administrative districts, two cities, and five towns. These are administered by 17 local authorities (district councils, city councils or town councils).


As well as the main districts, Botswana also has seven urban districts which comprise the area of cities and towns.
